_sText: You've turned to the sewers for refuge; however, you're not alone in your decisions. wander the dark tunnels of the sewer and find a good hiding spot before things all go to hell. this is a really large 32 man map that plays out a bit like a game of sardines. the map is dark and there's enough hiding spots to keep yourself safe for.. well, at least a few minutes. a .vmf is located below for your editing pleasures. http://www.fpsbanana.com/mips/68 VIDEO LINK
